Respectively: intrans. and trans. Also -u-sɨ-rɨnma-; -u-su-winma-, intrans. Other transitive verbs are -ɨpunpəʔma-; -uwinma-; -ɨrɨnma-. 'To shake dice' is -əəwa. The forms depend on type of movement and material.

Respectively: intrans. and trans. Also -u-sɨ-rɨnma-; -u-su-winma-, intrans. Other transitive verbs are -ɨpunpəʔma-; -uwinma-; -ɨrɨnma-. 'To shake dice' is -əəwa. The forms depend on type of movement and material.

Intransitive form. Also transitives: -ɨkareka-; -ɨkərə-; -uwəntare-čaka-, the latter to tear the edge (of something).
